# cppcheck configuration for Sovereign System verification components
# Focus: security, memory, portability issues in cryptographic and verifier code
# Suppress third-party or generated code noise.

# Paths to ignore (external libs, test data, vendored headers)
-i deps/catch2/
-i deps/libsodium/
-i build/

# Enable comprehensive checks; style suppressed in CI context to reduce noise.
--enable=warning,performance,portability,information
--inconclusive

# Treat these patterns as library code (skip duplicate symbol / style spam)
--library=std
--suppress=missingIncludeSystem
--suppress=unusedFunction

# Exit code policy handled by script (run-static-analysis.sh)
